tweet: Today, @RepCasten and I spoke on the Floor in support of our bipartisan Resolution, which passed overwhelmingly. It is time to empower community partnerships and law enforcement in their work to safeguard seniors against deception and scams. More here: https://johnrose.house.gov/media/press-releases/rose-casten-bipartisan-resolution-support-combating-financial-exploitation …
Age brings many of life’s most difficult challenges, but financial exploitation should not be one of them.

It is time to equip our friends, families, and neighbors with the knowledge and tools they need to guard against the heartbreak of their hard-earned security and stability being stolen in the golden years of life. #financialliteracy
Tune in to @cspan now to hear my remarks on the House Floor regarding the importance of financial literacy for #TN6 seniors.
